Miss Carpe Diem: Diipa Büller-Khosla 

Her world is an enamel of glamour, coated with reality where she is a social media influencer, a mother, an advocate of human rights issues, a fashion icon, and now, a beautypreneur

 Representing the new age of success, Diipa Büller-Khosla in conversation with GlobalSpa opens up about her journey from courtrooms to red carpets, her hustle as a social media influencer, and the newest feather in her cap - “indē wild” - the world’s first Ayurverdistry brand.
