We’ve partnered with @advancedsimracing to test out this insane sim rig.

@thomasholland_th is a kid on Christmas morning right now.

@advancedsimracing does custom complete builds, and full white glove delivery and setup. They also manufacture high quality sim parts, And they designed and made a custom TH racing rig for us. It looks amazing.

Yesterday they delivered the whole rig, set it up and dialed it in. You can now expect to hear nothing from Thomas for many days.

More to come on this!

